Uses of Package
org.rcdukes.common

  • Packages that use org.rcdukes.common 
    Package Description
    org.rcdukes.action
    Action/Luke Verticle to control car based on detections org.rcdukes.action is part of the rc-action module StraightLaneNavigator
    org.rcdukes.app
    Initial JavaFx apps for Lane and StartLight Detection have been replaced by webcontrol in the meantime
    org.rcdukes.car
    org.rcdukes.car is part of the rc-car module Engine and Steering control on the device (Raspberry)
    org.rcdukes.common
    org.rcdukes.common is part of the rc-common module Configuration, DukesVerticle, Environment, ClusterStarter and Characters (e.g.
    org.rcdukes.detect
    org.rcdukes.detect is part of the rc-detect module
    org.rcdukes.drivecontrol
    org.rcdukes.drivecontrol is part of the rc-drivecontrol module it contains the classes to control the vehicle
    org.rcdukes.imageview
    org.dukes.imageview is part of the rc-imageview module Has the DebugImageServer and VideoRecorder
    org.rcdukes.remotecar
    org.rcdukes.remotecar is part of the rc-remotecar module RemoteCar verticle to run on client to receive commands via network
    org.rcdukes.server
    CarServer entry point to start cluster and webcontrol
    org.rcdukes.watchdog
    org.rcdukes.watchdog is part of the rc-watchdog module The Watchdog controls power - it will automatically power off if no heartbeat signal is received making sure the remote connection is alive
    org.rcdukes.webcontrol
    Web app to remotely control the RC car and e.g start/stop autopilot watch live camera screen and control engine, wheels and led
